Valeo Plans to Double China Revenue by 2015, China Daily Says

-- B y   B e i   H u
-- 
2011-04-02T03:26:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-02/valeo-plans-to-double-china-revenue-by-2015-china-daily-says.html
<a href="blpnews:linkid=582CSLBXAES4"> Valeo SA (FR) </a>, a French maker of
automotive components, plans to double revenue in  China  by 2015,
increasing investing in the country and strengthening research
and development, China Daily reported today.  Valeo had sales of $1 billion in China last year, the
English-language <a href="blpnews:linkid=8NA9P31RZUWZ">report</a> said. The Paris-based company plans to
invest as much as 500 million euro ($712 million) in China
during the next five years, it added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
